<reference id="chrow" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>chrow</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>chrow</keyword>&gt; element is a container inside the &lt;<keyword>choicetable</keyword>&gt; element.
The &lt;<keyword>chrow</keyword>&gt; element contains both a &lt;<keyword>choption</keyword>&gt; and &lt;<keyword>chdesc</keyword>&gt; element
as a pair.</shortdesc>
